  "texts": [
    "The submit button then remains disabled until the LLM generates its next response, which typically appears after about three seconds if responses are not streamed.",
    "Instead of waiting for the complete response to be produced before showing it, streaming responses display text progressively as the language model generates it.",
    "This feature preserves the user experience and conversational flow known from commercial chat applications, and thereby increases participant engagement and reduces the risk of non-random attrition.",
    "Simple Chat is well suited for online experiments across a wide range of research domains, including behavioral economics, cognitive psychology, and computational social science.",
    "It can also serve as a valuable tool for AI safety research."
